title: Pakistan ambassador in Belgium, DG EU Commission discuss ways to expand bilateral cooperation
content:
ISLAMABAD, Nov 3 (APP):Pakistan Ambassador to Belgium, Luxembourg and the EU Amna Baloch on Friday met with Director-General for Mobility and Transport at European Commission Magda Kopczynska and discussed matters relating to mutual interests.
During the meeting they discussed the ongoing engagement tracks and explored pathways to expand bilateral cooperation.
